description.en:
GINcoin's main purpose is to increase the likelihood of masternode mass adoption. It achieves this in two core ways:
I) By allowing non-technical users to deploy masternodes through a GUI-based, easy to use interface  (this has been available for some time now and it's our main driver)
II) By enabling users to pool their funds together and share a more expensive masternode - e.g. Dash (this feature is due this August)

We have a working platform ( https://p.gincoin.io/#!/ ) with over 1800 hosted masternodes ( market value over 10,000,000 USD ) and support for 17 coins. More will be added as we move forward.

GIN is the only coin we accept as payment for our services. It is used to pay for the hosting fee and will be used in our shared masternodes service.
